oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bar-N Ranch - Unknown date - Part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WLS Bar-N Ranch radio program, unknown broadcast date, part 1. Cast includes Red Foley, Aunt Sally Newcombe, Salty Holmes, Judy Martin, and the Boys From The Bunkhouse (including Russ, Ernie, and Charlie on fiddle), with announcer Jack Mitchell. Circa mid-1940s based on performances.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Red Foley; Boys From The Bunkhouse; Aunt Sally Newcombe; Salty Holmes; Judy Martin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Opening statement (Jack Mitchell) -- Theme (Cimarron (Roll On)) -- Jack Mitchell introduces Aunt Sally Newcombe -- Aunt Sally Newcombe introduces Red Foley -- Walking The Floor Over You (Red Foley) -- Aunt Sally Newcombe introduces Red Foley, Russ, and Ernie -- Tumbling Tumbleweeds (Red Foley, Russ, and Ernie) -- Red Foley introduces Aunt Sally Newcombe -- Lonesome Valley (Aunt Sally Newcombe vocals) -- Red Foley and Salty Holmes talk -- Blue Prairie (Red Foley) -- Comedy routine (Red Foley, Aunt Sally Newcombe, Salty Holmes, Judy Martin, Ernie) (incomplete) -- [re-record of ending]
